icDumpMode = "modified".
DEF VAR idLastDump    AS DEC  NO-UNDO.
DEF VAR icEventSource AS CHAR NO-UNDO.
DEF VAR icEventFields AS CHAR NO-UNDO.
DEF VAR oiEvents      AS INT  NO-UNDO.
DEF VAR olInterrupted AS LOG  NO-UNDO.


